Page.title: Hello world!
Page.description:
Yo! I’m Matheus, a coder during my free time… and, well, all the other times too (coding is basically my jam). I’m tight with TypeScript, and lately, I’ve been low-key vibing with Python – feels like it might be turning into a full-on thing.
On my blog, I keep it real with dev stories, wins, and the occasional “what the heck just happened?” moments. If you’re down for the ride, swing by and check it out! ✌️
